body:
This mod is an alternative to [InControl](https://modrinth.com/mod/in-control "InControl") and other spawning mods that allow you to add, remove, and modify living entity spawn conditions and spawn groups. Various conditions related to entities, biomes, dimensions, height, light, and gamestages can be checked for before spawning while armor, tools, weapons, attributes can be modified after spawning. Spawn entry modification is done in a vanilla-friendly manner in an effort to ensure compatibility whenever possible.
&nbsp;     

Everything is handled through a single TOML-based config file found at config/specifiedspawning.toml.   
&nbsp;     

For a more complete guide of the mod check out the [wiki](https://github.com/TheComputerizer/Specified-Spawning/wiki "wiki")

